# AI Core

Read `docs/ai-core.md` before changes.

## Module map

- `agents/runtime/` — AgentMemory, AgentTools, UnifiedAgentContext, ContextBuilder
- `application/intelligence/personality_service.py` — PersonalityService (not in prompts)
- `application/intelligence/ugra_mood.py` — UI labels (🐆 На охоте...)
- `application/autonomous/first_task.py` — startup autonomy
- `application/events/handlers.py` — event subscriptions

## Interfaces

- `IAgentTool` = `AgentTool` in `core/tools/base.py`
- `ILLMProvider` = `LLMCompletionPort` in `infrastructure/llm/ports.py`
- `AgentOrchestrator` = `IntelligenceOrchestrator`

## Prompts

Use `prompts/{agent}.md` — never hardcode in Python.

## Memory

Persist via `AgentMemory.record_*()` — not raw repository in agents.
